<sect1 id="index_1autotoc_md1">
<title>Usage</title>
<para>Clone (as a submodule or otherwise): <programlisting filename=".shell"><codeline><highlight class="normal">git<sp/>submodule<sp/>add<sp/>git@github.com:nvsl/cpp-common.git<sp/>vendor/cpp-common</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>Add the directory as a include directory: <programlisting filename=".shell"><codeline><highlight class="normal">g++<sp/>-iquote&quot;vendor/cpp-common/include&quot;<sp/>main.cc<sp/>-o<sp/>main</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>Use the files in your project: <programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="preprocessor">#include<sp/>&quot;<ref refid="string_8hh" kindref="compound">nvsl/string.hh</ref>&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="preprocessor">#include<sp/>&lt;iostream&gt;</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">int</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>main()<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordflow">for</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>(</highlight><highlight class="keyword">const</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">auto</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>tok<sp/>:<sp/><ref refid="string_8hh_1a0e3a85c1cd47991d7ac6cbca8e5edc63" kindref="member">split</ref>(</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;Hello!<sp/>World.&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;<sp/>&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">))<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>std::cout<sp/>&lt;&lt;<sp/>tok<sp/>&lt;&lt;<sp/>std::endl;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">}</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>Prints: <programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">Hello!</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">World</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect1>
